{
  "dialogue": {
    "Oh! Aren't you the one who just moved in?": ["Introduction"],
    "I'm Maru. I've been looking forward to meeting you!": ["Introduction_sv1"],
    "You know, with a small town like this, a new face can really alter the community dynamic. It's exciting!": [
      "Introduction_sv2"
    ],
    "Heh... sure! Suddenly, the dance sounds a lot more fun.": [
      "FlowerDance_Accept"
    ],
    "Hey, what's this, a birthday gift? It's great! Thanks for remembering me!": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive"
    ],
    "Hey, what's this, a birthday gift? It's... uh, well, it's a gift! Thanks for remembering me, anyway.": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative"
    ],
    "Mmm... How does it taste so good? This is really a great gift.": [
      "AcceptGift_StardropTea"
    ],
    "This will be perfect for powering my latest project! Thanks, @!": [
      "AcceptGift_787"
    ],
    "Ah, pure gold... It's not the strongest material, but it has some really useful properties!": [
      "AcceptGift_336"
    ],
    "Oh, wow! That's a rare element. It's theorized that all the iridium in our world comes from meteorites...": [
      "AcceptGift_337"
    ],
    "Ooh, this is exciting! I'll deconstruct it and see if I can reverse-engineer the technology.": [
      "AcceptGift_122"
    ],
    "Ahh! Be careful with that! Are you touching it with your bare hands?": [
      "AcceptGift_910"
    ],
    "... Sorry... hehe... With proper handling, this will be perfect for an exotic machine I'm building.": [
      "AcceptGift_910_sv1"
    ],
    "Ummm... Don't break the news to my Dad, okay? I'll handle it.": [
      "dating_Maru"
    ],
    "Mmm... I'm having a hard time focusing on my work today.": [
      "dating_Maru_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "I want to go collect samples with my dad, but my Mom is insisting we stay here...": [
      "GreenRain"
    ],
    "This is a rare opportunity to study a unique phenomenon... every moment counts!": [
      "GreenRain_2"
    ],
    "I should've spent more time on that piece before showing you...": [
      "eventSeen_9"
    ],
    "How's your hand feeling?": ["eventSeen_9_memory_oneweek"],
    "Let me see it... Hey, it looks all better!": [
      "eventSeen_9_memory_oneweek_sv1"
    ],
    "Hey, I guess we're brother and sister now!": [
      "married_Sebastian_male_farmer"
    ],
    "Hey, I guess we're sisters now!": ["married_Sebastian_female_farmer"],
    "I'm glad that Sebastian found a way out of the basement...": [
      "married_Sebastian_sv1"
    ],
    "I wish you two all the best!": ["married_Sebastian_sv2"],
    "Hey, congratulations!": ["married_Penny"],
    "I remember the first time Penny told me she had feelings for you...": [
      "married_Penny_sv1"
    ],
    "She was all shy about it, but I knew right away it was serious... she wouldn't say something like that if she didn't mean it!": [
      "married_Penny_sv2"
    ],
    "You always seemed far too healthy to be at the clinic so often... Now it's all starting to make sense...": [
      "married_Harvey"
    ],
    "Willy mentioned that you helped fix the boat. Thanks for doing that!": [
      "Resort_Entering"
    ],
    "That was fun!": ["Resort_Leaving"],
    "I've been noticing a few different starfish species. My favorite are the big purple ones, but they're all very interesting!": [
      "Resort"
    ],
    "*gasp*... It's a solar eclipse!": ["Resort_Towel"],
    "Oh... never mind. It's just your body blocking the sun.": [
      "Resort_Towel_sv1"
    ],
    "We're so far removed from civilization out here.": ["Resort_Towel_2"],
    "Imagine the stars you could see at night.": ["Resort_Towel_2_sv1"],
    "Who knows, maybe we'd even see a flying saucer or two!": [
      "Resort_Towel_2_sv2"
    ],
    "Mmmm... Why are tropical fruits so good?": ["Resort_Bar"],
    "I wonder if Willy would let me bring my telescope here sometime...The sky is so clear here, I bet I could spot Pelican Town out in the horizon.Maybe I'd even see you running around %farm Farm!": [
      "Resort_Shore"
    ],
    "Of course... *whisper* Then can we go home and snuggle?": [
      "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse"
    ],
    "I'm flattered! But... No.": ["FlowerDance_Decline"],
    "We have nothing to say to each other.": ["divorced"],
    "Not good enough for you, huh?": ["breakUp"],
    "Fine...": ["breakUp_sv1"],
    "You've got some nerve, speaking to me!": ["dumped_Girls"],
    "You've lost some respect with me, @... but I'm willing to forgive you.": [
      "secondChance_Girls"
    ],
    "Whenever I'm struggling with a technical problem, I always take a walk.": [
      "Mon"
    ],
    "It's surprising how much a change of scenery can help.": ["Mon_sv1"],
    "Have you met my mother? She's the town's carpenter.": ["Tue"],
    "On Tuesdays and Thursdays I work at Harvey's clinic.": ["Wed"],
    "He says he likes having me around in case his medical equipment goes haywire!": [
      "Wed_sv1"
    ],
    "Being a farmer must be pretty easy, huh?": ["Wed_sv2"],
    "I plan on spending a lot of time with my telescope this summer.": ["Thu"],
    "Sometimes, when I'm looking into space with my telescope, I get struck with this eerie feeling... Like we aren't meant to see this.": [
      "Thu4"
    ],
    "It's silly, I know...": ["Thu4_sv1"],
    "Do you know my Dad, Demetrius? He's a scientist. I have a lot of fun helping him out in the laboratory.": [
      "Sat"
    ],
    "It's really satisfying when you can repair something yourself, instead of just throwing it away.": [
      "Sat2"
    ],
    "Some people say 'magic isn't real'... but have they ever stopped and really thought about magnetism?": [
      "Sat4"
    ],
    "If you think about the human body, it's hard to believe that somehow, it all just 'works'.": [
      "Sat6"
    ],
    "You know, I was thinking... even with all the technology in the world, nothing beats having a real human friend.": [
      "Sat8"
    ],
    "Hey, sorry if I seem cranky... I'm a little sore from work yesterday.": [
      "Fri"
    ],
    "I had to carry ten boxes of medical files to the attic!": [
      "Fri_sv1_chance_1"
    ],
    "I had to sort patient records for four hours straight!": [
      "Fri_sv1_chance_2"
    ],
    "Hi!": ["Sun"],
    "Do you have fun working on the farm?": ["Sun_sv1"],
    "Hey, you've made another week of progress on the farm! It seems like things are going well for you.": [
      "Sun_01_old_prereq_1"
    ],
    "Another tiring week on the farm, huh? It must really be a lot of work...": [
      "Sun_01_old_prereq_2"
    ],
    "Well that's good, isn't it?": ["Sun_01_01"],
    "Yikes! I'm sorry. Have you ever thought of doing something different...?": [
      "Sun_01_02"
    ],
    "Stop by our house when you need to upgrade your buildings.": ["Tue2"],
    "It's always nice to have visitors.": ["Tue2_sv1"],
    "My mother is a carpenter and my dad is a scientist. I guess it makes sense that I'm into building gadgets.": [
      "Fri4"
    ],
    "My Dad is very logical, and my Mom is very intuitive. That difference leads to conflict, sometimes...": [
      "Fri6"
    ],
    "Sometimes my head gets so cluttered with nonsense I can hardly think. Does that ever happen to you?": [
      "Mon6"
    ],
    "Getting some fresh air usually helps.": ["Mon6_sv1"],
    "I'm glad to have a job at the clinic... I feel like I'm helping people in town.": [
      "Wed8"
    ],
    "Dr. Harvey? He's nice, but not really my type...": ["Wed8_sv1"],
    "Oh, @! Is there anything you want to talk to me about?": ["Thu10"],
    "Of course he'll know the difference! This sample is completely ruined!%fork": [
      "Event_Hospital_1"
    ],
    "Okay. I'll blame it on you, then.": ["Event_Hospital_2"],
    "You're right. I should just tell him the truth.%fork": [
      "Event_Hospital_3"
    ],
    "It's amazing, isn't it?": ["Event_Space1"],
    "I guess you could see it like that...": ["Event_Space2"],
    "But it's still incredible, isn't it?": ["Event_Space2_sv1"],
    "Oh no?": ["Event_Cut1"],
    "Well, that makes me feel a little better, then. Thanks.": [
      "Event_Cut1_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh no! Aghh... I'm really really sorry.": ["Event_Cut2"],
    "Thanks. That means a lot to me, @.": ["event_robot1"],
    "I know gadgets aren't really your kind of thing... but I do appreciate that you're showing interest in what I do.": [
      "event_robot1_sv1"
    ],
    "I wish I could return the favor somehow.": ["event_robot1_sv2"],
    "What? After she said point-blank that she doesn't want to be a slave? How cold...%fork": [
      "event_robot2"
    ],
    "Heh...": ["event_robot3"],
    "Yeah I guess he did kinda say that, didn't he?": ["event_robot3_sv1"],
    "...Um...": ["event_robot3_sv2"],
    "...": ["event_robot4", "event_robot_explain1", "fall_Thu10_sv1"],
    "@...": ["event_robot4_sv1"],
    "@": ["event_robot4_sv2"],
    "You have a point, I did program her to act human... but her neural net is so complex, I can't be sure consciousness didn't emerge on its own.": [
      "event_robot_explain1_sv1"
    ],
    "Furthermore, isn't it a little arrogant to assume that human-like consciousness is the only worthwhile vessel of existence? Computer brains are different than ours, but that doesn't mean we can disregard them.": [
      "event_robot_explain1_sv2"
    ],
    "I see. Well it wasn't a very funny joke.": ["event_robot_explain2"],
    "That's horrible! What's gotten into you, @?": ["event_robot_explain3"],
    "I'm just going to forget about this conversation... you aren't acting yourself.": [
      "event_robot_explain3_sv1"
    ],
    "This is going to be a great season for stargazing.": ["summer_1"],
    "Hmm... What sort of gadget should I tinker with this summer?": [
      "summer_Mon"
    ],
    "Come to my room if you ever want to tinker with my gadgets.": [
      "summer_Mon6"
    ],
    "Sebastian is my half-brother, if you didn't know already.": ["summer_Tue"],
    "We look totally different.": ["summer_Tue_sv1"],
    "Sebastian hardly ever talks to me. I wonder if he even likes me at all?": [
      "summer_Tue4"
    ],
    "It's sad, I want to have a brother but he doesn't act like one.": [
      "summer_Tue4_sv1"
    ],
    "Are you enjoying the season?": ["summer_Wed"],
    "It's been so warm this year.": ["summer_Wed_sv1"],
    "Penny and I have been doing a seasonal book club.": ["summer_Wed4"],
    "It's just the two of us, but it's still fun to discuss what we're reading!": [
      "summer_Wed4_sv1"
    ],
    "Sorry, I was just thinking about some gadgets I'm making.": ["summer_Thu"],
    "I've decided I'm going to build a robot someday.": ["summer_Thu_sv1"],
    "See you later.": ["Thu_01_old"],
    "Really? Are you sure you're not just trying to flatter me?": ["Thu_0"],
    "You don't think I could do it?": ["Thu_01_01"],
    "You're right, but I love a challenge!": ["Thu_01_02"],
    "Hey, have any interesting farm stories to tell me?": ["summer_Sat"],
    "Guess not.": ["summer_Sat_sv1"],
    "I worked at the clinic yesterday. We didn't have a single patient.": [
      "summer_Fri"
    ],
    "I guess people get sick less during summer.": ["summer_Fri_sv1"],
    "I bet you're growing some interesting crops right now.": ["summer_Sun"],
    "Dad says a lot of exotic plants grow in the valley this time of year.": [
      "summer_Sun_sv1"
    ],
    "Hey, tell me a story about farming.": ["summer_Fri2"],
    "That's really interesting!": ["summer_Fri2_sv1"],
    "Is it just me or did it suddenly get really hot?": ["summer_Wed2"],
    "I guess it's just me.": ["summer_Wed2_sv1"],
    "Some day I'm going to be a world-class inventor.": ["summer_Sun6"],
    "You're lucky to be friends with me!": ["summer_Sun6_sv1"],
    "...just kidding.": ["summer_Sun6_sv2"],
    "@, you're looking sharp today.": ["summer_Tue8"],
    "How do your hands stay so soft with all that farm work?": ["summer_Thu10"],
    "Have you explored the mines much? I've heard you can find some useful materials there.": [
      "fall_Mon"
    ],
    "The trees look beautiful today!": ["fall_Tue"],
    "In other parts of the world it's spring right now. Imagine that!": [
      "fall_Thu"
    ],
    "Bleh... I don't feel like working tomorrow.": ["fall_Wed"],
    "I bet we'll start seeing more people at the clinic this season.": [
      "fall_Fri"
    ],
    "I hope everyone stays healthy.": ["fall_Fri_sv1"],
    "All these falling leaves will provide food for mushrooms and other small organisms.": [
      "fall_Sat"
    ],
    "Interesting, isn't it?": ["fall_Sat_sv1"],
    "Hey, here's to another good week! *toast*": ["fall_Sun"],
    "@, I just love how the trees look right now!": ["fall_Tue2"],
    "I know you like them too.": ["fall_Tue2_sv1"],
    "If you have any extra metal laying around, I could always use it for one of my projects.": [
      "fall_Wed4"
    ],
    "But only if you don't need it yourself.": ["fall_Wed4_sv1"],
    "I've been feeling especially optimistic lately...": ["fall_Fri6"],
    "You should come visit me at the clinic tomorrow. I work from 10 a.m. to 4 p.m.": [
      "fall_Mon8"
    ],
    "You have a leaf in your hair. Let me get it for you.": ["fall_Thu10"],
    "Oh man, it's so cold...": ["winter_1"],
    "Did you see the snowman I built?": ["winter_Mon"],
    "My hair gets so frizzy in this dry weather. *sigh*": ["winter_Tue"],
    "I guess winter is a good time to work on my gadgets.": ["winter_Wed"],
    "I wonder if I could make anything useful for farmers?": ["winter_Wed_sv1"],
    "Hey! What's up?": ["winter_Thu"],
    "It's a good time to explore the caves.": ["winter_Thu_sv1"],
    "I would go but my Dad would flip.": ["winter_Thu_sv2"],
    "I hope I don't catch the flu this year.": ["winter_Fri"],
    "Have you built a furnace yet?": ["winter_Sat"],
    "You can use them to turn raw material like ores into more useful products.": [
      "winter_Sat_sv1"
    ],
    "I get so sleepy when it's cold...": ["winter_Sun"],
    "Hey, if any of your farming machines need to be fixed, just let me know.": [
      "winter_Sat2"
    ],
    "Hey, do you have any ideas for a new gadget I can make?": ["winter_Tue4"],
    "Mhmm. I trust your opinion.": ["winter_Tue4_sv1"],
    "You look fresh today. I guess it's that crisp winter air.": [
      "winter_Fri6"
    ],
    "Hi @!": ["winter_Mon8"],
    "Hey, don't you think my snowman looks kind of like you?": [
      "winter_Mon8_sv1"
    ],
    "@, come closer. I'm cold.": ["winter_Thu10"],
    "My hands are so dry from the winter air. I'm sorry about that.": [
      "winter_Thu10_sv1"
    ]
  },
  "marriage_dialogue": {
    "I wonder how Penny is doing? Maybe I'll give her a call later today.": [
      "Rainy_Day_0"
    ],
    "I was just daydreaming... do you think MARILDA is okay? I hope she finds some place where she truly belongs...": [
      "Rainy_Day_1"
    ],
    "Hey! I had trouble sleeping last night so I fiddled around in my workshop for a bit. Here, I made this for you.": [
      "Rainy_Day_2"
    ],
    "I hope you can find some use for it.": ["Rainy_Day_2_sv1"],
    "The only thing I dislike about rain is the fact that I can't do any stargazing!": [
      "Rainy_Day_3"
    ],
    "Do I hear a leak in the roof? I'll have to check it out. I know a thing or two about carpentry from watching my mother.": [
      "Rainy_Day_4"
    ],
    "Make sure you don't leave your tools out in the rain! You wouldn't want them to get all rusty.": [
      "Rainy_Night_0"
    ],
    "I'm not sure what this is, yet... but it's fun to turn the old wrench now and then.": [
      "patio_Maru"
    ],
    "Hi @. How was your day... soggy?": ["Rainy_Night_1"],
    "This weather gives me gadget ideas... maybe if I funnel the rainwater it could power a mill?": [
      "Rainy_Night_1_sv1"
    ],
    "Dad's been tracking the weather patterns for the last twenty years.": [
      "Rainy_Night_2"
    ],
    "It's a little too early to tell, but the results have revealed some abnormal trends.": [
      "Rainy_Night_2_sv1"
    ],
    "Can we have spaghetti in bed tonight?": ["Rainy_Night_3"],
    "I made some dessert! Make sure to brush your teeth before bed, though.": [
      "Rainy_Night_4"
    ],
    "My day wasn't all that exciting... I stayed inside because of the weather.": [
      "Rainy_Night_5"
    ],
    "It was relaxing, though. I kicked back with the latest 'Schematics Weekly'.": [
      "Rainy_Night_5_sv1"
    ],
    "Hmm? Sorry, sometimes I get so lost in thought that I don't even realize what I'm doing.": [
      "Indoor_Day_0"
    ],
    "I found this in my scrap pile. Think you could find a use for it?": [
      "Indoor_Day_1"
    ],
    "Finally, you're up! I was getting so hungry... *rumble*": ["Indoor_Day_2"],
    "One of the best things about living on the farm is waking up to a chorus of songbirds.": [
      "Indoor_Day_3"
    ],
    "How do you keep your hands so soft with all that farm work?": [
      "Indoor_Day_4"
    ],
    "Did you see the moon tonight? It always looks spectacular on the horizon.": [
      "Indoor_Night_0"
    ],
    "I saw a shooting star earlier. I like to pretend it's MARILDA stopping by to check on us.": [
      "Indoor_Night_1"
    ],
    "I can't decide if I'm craving chocolate cake or ripe strawberries. Or maybe both...?": [
      "Indoor_Night_2"
    ],
    "Be honest... am I gaining weight?": ["Indoor_Night_2_sv1"],
    "You did good work today! You deserve to relax the rest of the evening.": [
      "Indoor_Night_3"
    ],
    "I'm really starting to love this old house. It's so cozy at night.": [
      "Indoor_Night_4"
    ],
    "Mom's done a great job improving the place.": ["Indoor_Night_4_sv1"],
    "Ahh... the farm smells great, it reminds me of the mountains near my parent's house.": [
      "Outdoor_0"
    ],
    "With a little planning, we could automate most of the farm work and just relax!": [
      "Outdoor_1"
    ],
    "It's going to be clear tonight... I wonder if the %noun constellation will be visible?": [
      "Outdoor_2"
    ],
    "Don't worry, I won't mind if you track mud into the house. It's fun to get a little dirty now and then.": [
      "Outdoor_3"
    ],
    "I never realized the amount of care and planning necessary to run a farm! It's a lot like working in the laboratory.": [
      "Outdoor_4"
    ],
    "Have you spent any time with %kid1 today? Kids need playtime in order reach their full potential.": [
      "OneKid_0"
    ],
    "What do you think... will %kid1 grow up to be a farmer? Or an engineer?": [
      "OneKid_1"
    ],
    "I have high hopes for our child. I've been reading all the scientific data on the best ways to raise children.": [
      "OneKid_3"
    ],
    "My own workshop, two wonderful kids, and a beautiful plot of land. Life is pretty good.": [
      "TwoKids_3"
    ],
    "Now that we live together, it's hard to imagine being alone again.": [
      "Good_1"
    ],
    "Taking a break? That's good!": ["Good_2"],
    "There's a lot of strategy to planning and running a farm. It's more intellectually stimulating than I thought!": [
      "Good_3"
    ],
    "For a while there I was considering building a robotic husband. But you're a lot more fun!": [
      "Good_4_male_farmer"
    ],
    "For a while there I was considering building a robotic wife. But you're a lot more fun!": [
      "Good_4_female_farmer"
    ],
    "I was just admiring my wedding amulet... The shell is flawless. This is a very rare specimen!": [
      "Good_5"
    ],
    "Last night, I had a dream that I was looking through a gigantic telescope. I saw something moving in the %noun nebula. Kind of spooky.": [
      "Good_6"
    ],
    "I hope you'd still like me even if I gained weight.": ["Neutral_0"],
    "I feel uninspired today.": ["Neutral_8"],
    "I think I'll visit my parents today. I haven't seen them in a while.": [
      "funLeave_Maru"
    ],
    "Mom and Dad are doing just fine. Their routine is still the same, even with me gone. How was your day?": [
      "funReturn_Maru"
    ],
    "So, what's your strategy for optimizing the farm this year?": ["spring_2"],
    "It's wonderful to see all the plants and animals come back to life during the spring.": [
      "spring_1"
    ],
    "If my brother wasn't such a hermit I'd invite him over for dinner sometime.": [
      "spring_22"
    ],
    "I wonder if my brother will ever have the courage to ask Abigail out?": [
      "summer_20"
    ],
    "I like to catalogue the different insects I see in summer.": ["summer_2"],
    "With every season, a new section of the night sky becomes prominent. It's fascinating to witness.": [
      "fall_1"
    ],
    "Winter's just around the corner. We need to double check the heating system, turn off the valves, and check all the insulation in the house.": [
      "fall_25"
    ],
    "Don't worry, dear. I'll take care of it all.": ["fall_25_sv1"],
    "Fall always reminds me of going out woodcutting with my mom... it might be that smell of freshly cut wood and sap.": [
      "fall_3"
    ],
    "The winters have been disturbingly mild lately.": ["winter_15"],
    "I hope Dad's doing okay... he can get depressed in winter, when there's less opportunity for field research.": [
      "winter_5"
    ],
    "So, what are your plans for maintaining our income this winter?": [
      "winter_2"
    ],
    "You could do some fishing or foraging...": ["winter_2_sv1"],
    "If you do any mining, promise me you'll be careful.": ["winter_2_sv2"],
    "I'm feeling excited for a new year of farming, @!": ["spring_Maru"],
    "The evenings are so warm, it's really the best time of year for stargazing. Who knows what might up there?": [
      "summer_Maru"
    ],
    "The farm life is great, but I'm glad I still work at the clinic... It's an important service for the community.": [
      "fall_Maru"
    ],
    "I'm really looking forward to having rhubarb pie in the spring. Oh... that tang, that zest!": [
      "winter_Maru"
    ],
    "I got up early to do a little stargazing.": ["spouseRoom_Maru_chance_1"],
    "I hope you don't mind if I spend some time on my projects today, honey.": [
      "spouseRoom_Maru_chance_2"
    ]
  },
  "gift_tastes": {
    "Is that...? Oh wow, @! This is spectacular!": ["MaruGiftTaste_1"],
    "This is a super gift! Thank you!": ["MaruGiftTaste_2"],
    "Oh... That's for me? I'll just put it over here...": ["MaruGiftTaste_3"],
    "Yuck! You thought I would like this?": ["MaruGiftTaste_4"],
    "Thanks.": ["MaruGiftTaste_5"]
  },
  "misc": {
    "Do you have an appointment?": ["Hospital_Maru_Greeting1"],
    "Can I help you?": ["Hospital_Maru_Greeting2"],
    "We've got medicine for sale!": ["Hospital_Maru_Greeting3"],
    "Is it an emergency?": ["Hospital_Maru_Greeting4"],
    "Here to see the doctor?": ["Hospital_Maru_Greeting5"],
    "Hi, @ <3": ["Hospital_Maru_Spouse"],
    "Hey! I'm looking forward to this one... I hope we learn a lot!": [
      "Maru_spring_movie_1_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "Ah, I see... that's very interesting!": [
      "Maru_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie"
    ],
    " *Maru's taking notes!*": ["Maru_spring_movie_1_DuringMovie_2"],
    "That was really interesting! I had no idea that so much life could be found in the big city.": [
      "Maru_spring_movie_1_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "It's a sci-fi movie, right? One of the things I like about sci-fi is seeing all the weird technologies they come up with.": [
      "Maru_summer_movie_1_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "Well, I've never seen anything like *that* through my telescope... but it was really great.": [
      "Maru_summer_movie_1_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "I really like going to the theater, even if the movie's bad!": [
      "Maru_like_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "That was an interesting choice, for the final scene. What do you think they meant by that?": [
      "Maru_like_AfterMovie"
    ],
